Author: waystosaygoodbye33
Text: I’ve been in the SAME place. I was just on three courses of antibiotics and one of them made me so so sick!! It’s hard because the anxiety makes it worse, and you don’t know what’s what :(  Feel better soon!

Author: xStingx
Text: I have no safe foods anymore thanks to bulimia. Anything that comes in MUST come out. Doesn't matter if its rice cakes, carrots, celery or raisins.  Anything with calories is pretty unsafe for me. I try to hold off on eating until I can't take it anymore.
